WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Welcome to UpliftiQ, where captions are treated as primary learning content.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.000
Learners can read large text in a dedicated caption panel with strong contrast.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.500
The full transcript stays clickable, so each moment is easy to revisit.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.500
Visual alerts, timers, and sign-ready playback extend the lesson beyond audio cues.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:19.500
Accessibility Mode can enlarge captions, expand the transcript, and simplify the layout in one step.
